{"id":1222,"date":"2025-04-10T01:06:08","date_gmt":"2025-04-09T18:06:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1222"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:40:32","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:40:32","slug":"oxyjet-dien-di-phuc-hoi-corticoid","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/oxyjet-dien-di-phuc-hoi-corticoid\/","title":{"rendered":"Oxy jet &#038; \u0111i\u1ec7n di ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i corticoid"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid, da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Oxy Jet v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p oxy tinh khi\u1ebft n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 98%. Khi phun v\u00e0o da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n t\u00e1ch th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1t s\u01b0\u01a1ng Oxy c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh nm, h\u1ea1t Oxy nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p thu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t nhanh, th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c, tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec7n di l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c ion ph\u00e2n t\u1eed HA trong tinh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc GSC Hyaluronic Serum th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0o s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec da. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111a, mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, th\u00e0nh h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 60 &#8211; 90 ph\u00fat.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb 03 &#8211; 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 07 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -4px; top: 93.3153px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00e0nh cho da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid, da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3596,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[59],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1222","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-advanced-skincare-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1222","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1222"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3596"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1222"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1222"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1222"},{"taxonomy":"product